title: Preaching Alabama S01E01 Meet The Speegles WEB-DL x264-RKSTR mp4
description:
The Speegles are a family of non-traditional preachers who heard the calling from up above to start a brand new church in Alabama. Eldest daughter, Jill, is taking lead as head pastor, as the family leaves everything behind to embark on their spiritual mission. With acceptance as their motto, this family welcomes everyone, and is praying that Alabama welcomes them too.
